					<li id="dsq-comment-7039">
					<div id="dsq-comment-header-7039" class="dsq-comment-header">
						<cite id="dsq-cite-7039">
	http://pixelwareinc.com							<span id="dsq-author-user-7039">Eric Anderson</span>
